<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="192" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="5.[113,752,193,248]" pageId="5" pageNumber="192">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[113,270,193,217]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="192">Etymology. –</emphasis>
The specific name refers to the straight apophysis of palpal tibia.
